| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0193 — Recovery Inhibition (darkpower)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b21c92ac-f6a5-5e1a-b8d8-1e05983c28fa"
